name: Kurt Cobain, Nirvana: Raji’s, Los Angeles, 2/15/90
description: An unpublished photo from Nirvana’s legendary Raji’s show, a real dive club in Hollywood. TAD opened, and slayed, and then Nirvana came on and obliterated. That is Donita Sparks from L7 down in front, swinging her hair. I love the opposing force between the direction her hair swing and Kurt’s. - Charles Peterson
